@NODE "Thing" "What is Wålly?"
@TOC "MAIN"



          Wålly the Wörrm is a new version of the old classic Worm-game.
"It's so easy to play that even YOU should be able to pick it up in no time."

By the way, Wålly the Wörrm is the swedish way of spelling Wally the Worm.
   

              BEHOLD!     WÅLLY THE WÖRRM IS FREEWARE!!!

  
