       Techno.
       ~~~~~~~
       It doesn't actually have very much to do with the music style
       we just thought that it was ehh.. a nice name..

       Note: This is probably the easiest level.

          
       Chains.
       ~~~~~~~
       Oooh.. this is a scary one.
          
       Note: This should be the hardest level as it forces you to go
       in the diagonal directions. There's not too much space either.


